                        {
                          "title": "Understanding Big and Little Endian Byte Order",
                          "url": "https://www.digital-detective.net/understanding-big-and-little-endian-byte-order/",
                          "snippet": "We agree that the difference between sending eggs with the little, or the big-end first is trivial, but we insist that everyone must do it in the same way, to avoid anarchy. Since the difference is trivial we may choose either way, but a decision must be made.",
                          "publishedDate": 1533736293000,
                          "id": "5",
                          "domain": "digital-detective.net",
                          "maxVerbatimWordLimit": 30,
