  "transcript": [
    "> /model",
    "> 在目录/Users/wangmu0579/DevEcoStudioProjects中帮我写一个鸿蒙手机版本的ftp server，自己上网搜索ftp server的具体功能",
    "\n\nLet me first research FTP server protocol details and HarmonyOS app development, then check the target directory.\n[Tool uses: web_search,web_search,fs_read]",
    "> t",
    "> t",
    "我看到你已经有一个 `ftpServer` 项目了。让我先看看现有项目的结构和代码，然后在此基础上完善。\n[Tool uses: fs_read]",
    "\n[Tool uses: fs_read,web_search]",
    "你已经有一个 ftpServer 项目了。让我先读取现有代码，了解当前实现状态。\n[Tool uses: fs_read]",
